comment:
* Read-only table that lists all the accounts that are used to provide bookmarks.
     * @hide

variables.name: ACCOUNT_NAME
variables.comment:
* The name of the account instance to which this row belongs, which when paired with * {@link #ACCOUNT_TYPE} identifies a specific account. *

Type: TEXT

variables.name: ACCOUNT_TYPE
variables.comment:
* The type of account to which this row belongs, which when paired with * {@link #ACCOUNT_NAME} identifies a specific account. *

Type: TEXT

variables.name: ROOT_ID
variables.comment:
* The ID of the account's root folder. This will be the ID of the folder * returned when querying {@link Bookmarks#CONTENT_URI_DEFAULT_FOLDER}. *

Type: INTEGER
